Package com.ilm.projecto_ilm_backend.dto.project

Class ProjectCreationDto

java.lang.Object
com.ilm.projecto_ilm_backend.dto.project.ProjectCreationDto
public class ProjectCreationDto extends Object
Data Transfer Object for creating a new project. This class encapsulates all necessary information required to create a new project, including its name, description, associated lab, required skills, interests (keywords), motivation for the project, start and end dates, project photo, and the maximum number of members.
